\begin_inset Formula $\forall\delta>0\ \omega_{T}(\delta)\geq C>0$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall n\ \omega_{T}(\frac{1}{n})\geq C>0$
\end_inset

, то есть 
