.
 Тогда 
\begin_inset Formula $||x_{n_{k}}'-x_{0}||\leq||x_{n_{k}}'-x_{n_{k}}||+||x_{n_{k}}-x_{0}||\leq\frac{1}{n_{k}}+||x_{n_{k}}-x_{0}||\to_{n_{k}\to\infty}0$
\end_inset

.
