\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
По индукции.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
База: 
\begin_inset Formula $n=1$
\end_inset

.
 Проверим: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f(x)-f(x_{0})=\int_{x_{0}}^{x}f'(t)dt=-\int_{x_{0}}^{x}f'(t)d(x-t)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f(x)=f(x_{0})-\left[f'(x)(x-t)|_{x_{0}}^{x}-\int_{x_{0}}^{x}f''(t)(x-t)dt\right]=\underbrace{f(x_{0})+f'(x_{0})(x-x_{0})}_{=T_{1}}+\int_{x_{0}}^{x}f''(t)(x-t)dt
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
Сделаем индукционный переход для 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

